<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我就來<delay8 />教你一招吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個嘛<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「笑哈哈」怎麼樣？<delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="10" b="12" /><size value="150" />啊哈哈！<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從丹田<delay8 />發出聲音大笑，<delay20 />
