<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也試試看吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="ColdChill" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個啊，<delay20 />在你聽到很冷的笑話時，<delay8 />
其實有個叫「咻～」的表情<delay8 />能派上用場<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你別一副<delay8 />沒興趣的樣子嘛，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別說那麼多，看就是了！<delay20 />我要做囉！<pageBreak /><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚～<delay20 />好冷<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實在好幾年前，<delay8 />有個完全不賣座的藝人，<delay frames="30" />
只要聽過那傢伙的冷笑話，<delay20 />
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家全都變成這個樣啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Apologize" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我來把我知道的表情<delay20 />
