<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不行，<delay20 />我完全想不到啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Apologize" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真抱歉喔！<delay frames="40" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />咦，<delay20 />剛才做的「鞠躬」表情……<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是還沒教過你？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
